Install Python App 
1. Open App play Store
2. Search "Python", found two App can be used
   QPython - Python for Android,  QPython3 - Python3 for Android
3. Install one of QPython and you can you can edit and run Python on Android Phone. 

4. QPython support two way to install python packages 
   4.1 Install with QPypi - Install packages that only Android Device (QPypi)
   4.2 Install with official pypi - Install pure Python Packages (pip console)
   
5. Packages that need to install using QPypi
   numpy  ---  last ver. 1.9.2                      # test ok on 16 Feb 2017
   
   

